  "instructions": [
    "Soak chestnuts in water for at least an hour to soften them.",
    "Preheat oven to 400\u00b0F (205\u00b0C).",
    "Peel garlic cloves and finely chop. Dice all mushrooms into small pieces.",
    "Mix olive oil, red wine vinegar, salt, pepper, and chopped garlic together in a mixing bowl.",
    "Drain chestnuts and place them on a baking sheet. Sprinkle the mushroom mix over the chestnuts evenly.",
    "Bake for 15 minutes or until the mushrooms are caramelized.",
    "Squeeze fresh parsley leaves over the top to garnish.",
    "Serve chilled as an appetizer."
